            "text": {
              "status": "generated",
              "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h3>Annotation</h3><table class=\"hl7__eu__lab__report\"><tr><th>Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us</th></tr><tr><td>The patient shows mildly elevated HbA1c, suggesting impaired glucose regulation or early diabetes, despite a low fasting glucose. Creatinine is slightly elevated, possibly indicating reduced renal function. Total CO₂ is low, which may suggest mild metabolic acidosis. Other parameters are within normal limits. Recommend clinical correlation for diabetes and renal function, and further evaluation of acid-base status.</td></tr></table></div>"
